        <tr><td>Annual maintenance contract</td><td>$280 to $440 per visit</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Multi-component repair</td><td>$900 to $1,800</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty</td><td>90 days parts plus labor</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 06 BRANDS WE SERVICE -->
<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">06 · Brands</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Convection oven brands we service.</h2>

    <ul class="brand-list">
      <li><strong>Vulcan</strong> (ITW Food Equipment Group). VC4 and VC6 the dominant LA install. Broad parts pipeline. <a href="/brands/vulcan-oven-repair/">Vulcan oven repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Blodgett</strong> (Middleby Corporation). Mark V (bakery favorite, belt-driven fan) and ZEPHAIRE. <a href="/brands/blodgett-oven-repair/">Blodgett oven repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Southbend</strong> (Middleby Corporation). Marathoner Gold series. <a href="/brands/southbend-oven-repair/">Southbend oven repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Garland</strong> (Welbilt). Master Series. Common in mid-tier restaurant kitchens. <a href="/brands/garland-range-repair/">Garland range repair brand page</a> (oven service available through same dispatch).</li>
      <li><strong>Bakers Pride</strong> (Standex Food Service). Cyclone series. <a href="/brands/bakers-pride-pizza-oven-repair/">Bakers Pride pizza oven repair brand page</a> (Cyclone service available through same dispatch).</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 07 WHY US -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Six reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Brand-specific failure pattern knowledge.</strong> Blodgett Mark V belt-drive vs Vulcan direct-drive vs Southbend Marathoner Gold ignition tree. Each has different diagnostic order.</li>
      <li><strong>Common parts on the van.</strong> Vulcan igniters, Blodgett drive belts, common thermostat models, door gaskets for major sizes.</li>
      <li><strong>Annual maintenance contracts.</strong> Predictable maintenance budget. Bakery and high-volume operations especially benefit.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS Licensed #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410).</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">licensing page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>$120 commercial diagnostic, no after-hours surcharge.</strong> Phones answered 24/7.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong> Next-day for Rancho Cucamonga and Temecula.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/commercial/oven-repair/combi-oven-repair/">combi oven repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/oven-repair/rotisserie-oven-repair/">rotisserie oven repair</a>. Parent: <a href="/commercial/oven-repair/">commercial oven repair pillar</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 08 FAQ -->
<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">08 · FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Convection oven repair, common questions.</h2>

    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map(f => (
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>{f.q}</summary>
          <p set:html={f.a} />
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 09 BOTTOM CTA -->
<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Convection oven down? Call today.</h2>
    <p>Blodgett, Vulcan, Southbend specialists. BHGS Licensed #A49573. $120 commercial diagnostic. Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href={phoneHref} class="btn-primary">☎ Call {phone}</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary">Book Online</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
